1.title: The Masseuse

episode of.title: Robot Apocalypse: The Early Years (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: Bruce needs a massage, but his regular masseuse, Mindy, is on vacation. He begrudgingly lets her replacement work his tired muscles. The big question is, will the replacement be up for a little "Deep Tissue"?

2.title: The Roboguard

episode of.title: Robot Apocalypse: The Early Years (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: Uncle Frank is hosting a BBQ for his nephew Tim and Tim's friends. Boys will be boys though, and rough housing turns to wrestling turns to leaping into the pool. Don't worry though, the trusty Roboguard is there to keep everything under control...

3.title: The Daycare Robot

episode of.title: Robot Apocalypse: The Early Years (TV Series 2010– )

3.plot: Where are you going to take your little ones when work beckons? Your friendly neighborhood Robo-daycare - that's where. Just be sure to give the attendants clear and concise instructions.
